#. <strong class="term">
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ay2:10.1"
msgid "Alañca kho hoti mātugāmaṃ duṭṭhullāhi vācāhi obhāsitunti"
msgstr ""

#. </strong><span class="gloss">
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ay2:10.2"
msgid "sakkā hoti mātugāmaṃ duṭṭhullāhi vācāhi obhāsituṃ."
